{"tid":1444783,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警狗新戰術","createTime":"2019-08-11T13:14:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T13:24:50.000Z","uid":270170,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1a66c3d357ba90c2f2c57e175d5cea949293e712","tid":1444783,"uid":270170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:14:19.000Z","msg":"就係分散兵力，靈活調動。<br />\n<br />\n今日夢遊左幾個地方(好撚攰)，發現每次防暴都出得好快，但人數好少。<br />\n<br />\n比起以前可能有三四排甚至更多既防暴，而家只係得返一兩排。<br />\n<br />\n佢地將兵力拆得咁散，可以分佈既地方會比較多，調動都更加快(一兩架狗車就得)。<br />\n<br />\n呢個戰術明顯係應對我地既遊擊戰，我地幾百人先消耗得佢地幾十個，其實好唔化算。<br />\n<br />\n集思下，我地係咪要轉陣，轉咩陣好？"},{"pid":"2a0d2ca109e88694afef141343ab09a41303c15b","tid":1444783,"uid":270170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:15:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b2fbc8dba882e02dd031e98ad4d7752326f70f82","tid":1444783,"uid":270170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:16:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c61e6270a21669797b55448bc4cd4353dcb4ac8","tid":1444783,"uid":270170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:16:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb91ce9d430c13dd9ea430b854e4fd20a6169963","tid":1444783,"uid":270170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:19:14.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n細佬蠢，比啲意見吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dad3255e0aeec58ed70f902d1cd5f0c60bea804","tid":1444783,"uid":270170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:21:16.000Z","msg":"推多3次"},{"pid":"7ea92487fef3388096752e97eec1986677c9699a","tid":1444783,"uid":270170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:22:37.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"1ed50af4ef652a1f3b19af216de60451915d816e","tid":1444783,"uid":270170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:24:50.000Z","msg":"1"}]}